text:
Tuğba Şenoğlu (born 2 February 1998) is a Turkish volleyball player.
She played at the 2015 Girls' Youth European Volleyball Championship, 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, 2017–18 CEV Women's Champions League, 2017 Women's European Volleyball Championship, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship.
She played for VakıfBank S.K.
